      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver benchmarked against canonical test cases with documented convergence behavior consistent with stated order of accuracy.",
      "rationale": "Fluent solver verified against lid-driven cavity and pipe flow benchmarks. Observed second-order spatial convergence confirmed in verification report VR-CODE-01."
