    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped to Gradation 1 per MRL 2 requirements and confirmed compliant. CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. RH < 1 acceptance criterion met across all evaluated operating points. Submission package accepted for regulatory decision support.",
